typing-inspection (0.4.2-0ubuntu1~ppa1~noble1) noble; urgency=medium

  * Initial packaging of typing-inspection 0.4.2 for the Avalan PPA.
  * Transitive runtime dep of python3-fastapi (also used by
    python3-pydantic). Not in Debian.
  * Ship a quilt patch (pyproject-license-for-noble) rewriting the
    PEP 639 `license = "MIT"` + `license-files = ['LICENSE']` pair
    to the legacy `license = { file = 'LICENSE' }` table form, the
    same Noble-hatchling workaround the rest of the per-dep tree
    uses.

 -- Avalan Packaging Team <avalan@avalan.ai>  Tue, 19 May 2026 00:35:00 -0300
